30:14.668 --> 30:15.089
Zero times.

30:15.189 --> 30:17.714
And this year I felt like I felt

30:17.858 --> 30:40.274
got was like you're gonna go past the Christmas like you might maybe with her voice her voice way heavy like all right and then family you want to go UK yes I know my people will know your people my people will think she's gonna be shopping that's why she's gonna go in the middle of service so leans over to me and she's like

30:40.354 --> 31:05.010
we're leading the uk and like no lily field is like and she's like no but we'll we'll be like the the represent like why she's like because we're gonna bring Bennett and we're gonna stay and we're gonna go to some time in games we're gonna do all this stuff I'm like if we're leading the trip we can't stay like extra like she's like no but like we're gonna go and then we'll just we'll pay extra to like stay I'm like who's gonna lead the team back for this day like soul is just like

31:05.282 --> 31:06.004
She's committed.

31:06.084 --> 31:08.310
