31:59.645 --> 32:13.362
I know pastor Fabio who's the pastor in Japan He has the desire because we're one of the teams that bring young people that brought young people the first two years So his hope and prayer is that because our trip is in the summer

32:13.570 --> 32:15.773
that a few more young people would be able to go.

32:16.274 --> 32:22.142
As the leader, I really don't want to try to keep alive other people's kids, but I did it last time so I guess I can do it again.

32:22.162 --> 32:32.978
And I would say like young people like 16 to 30 is a great range for Japan because

