35:34.080 --> 35:37.363
The best restaurant you're going to eat at is a long uphill walk.

35:38.024 --> 35:38.104
Wow.

35:38.124 --> 35:39.525
I think your grandmother went to school.

35:40.526 --> 35:44.210
I mean, we had, Zion was winded.

35:44.290 --> 35:44.991
on that walk.

35:45.672 --> 35:53.843
Zion is, you know, he's what, 19 now, a college student, physically fit, plays volleyball, and he was winded on that walk.

35:53.883 --> 35:55.646
So, yeah.

35:56.006 --> 35:58.249
It's a physical trip, but it's a good one.

35:58.269 --> 35:59.191
All right, you want to go in order?

